attributes.Long form description: The student changes the joy cons controllers to the comfort grip. Then, changes the joy cons to the joy con strap. Now, dissasembles the joy cons of the joy con strap to assembles to the Nintendo switch. Stands the Nintendo switch and changes the game card and the sd card. Lastly, turns on and off the Nintendo switch.
